<p>
Click an archive number to see an index of messages in that
archive, in the order of delivery.  
</p>
<h4 align="center">Search the Archives</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Choose a start date and/or end date for the messages you wish
  to search.
  <li>To search for messages posted from matching e-mail addresses, type 
  a pattern into the <b>Author</b> box.
  <li>To search for messages with matching subject lines, type a
  pattern into the <b>Subject</b> box.
  <li>Choose to display or mail the messages by pressing the
  appropriate button.
  <li>If you mail the messages, type an e-mail address into
  the last box.
  <li>Press the <b>Search</b> button.
</ul>

